    "body": "###### Reproduction Steps\r\n\r\n1. Have a filtered/custom study deck\r\n2. Go to card browser\r\n3. Tap the Deck spinner\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69634269/161396487-d3ffd3a9-0a8d-4336-98b8-eaf7967d1a35.mp4\r\n\r\n###### Expected Result\r\n\r\nFiltered decks and (maybe) custom decks dialog to appear on the deck selection dialog (anki desktop behavior)\r\n\r\n![2022_04_02-15_30_43](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69634269/161396539-65e162ff-4b53-401d-b023-e743159fc3cf.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n###### Actual Result\r\n\r\nThey only appear initially if selected on the deck picker, but not on the deck selection options, so it vanishes if user select another deck\r\n\r\n![2022_04_02-15_28_40](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69634269/161396699-8cbce847-a2d6-4e08-8e7d-cffd440912a8.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n###### Debug info\r\n```\r\nAnkiDroid Version = 2.16alpha54\r\n\r\nAndroid Version = 11\r\n\r\nManufacturer = samsung\r\n\r\nModel = SM-N770F\r\n\r\nHardware = exynos9810\r\n\r\nWebview User Agent = Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 11; SM-N770F Build/RP1A.200720.012; wv) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/99.0.4844.88 Mobile Safari/537.36\r\n\r\nACRA UUID = 037bbc86-38a4-4ad7-9c42-05870e9b6086\r\n\r\nScheduler = std2\r\n\r\nCrash Reports Enabled = true\r\n\r\nDatabaseV2 Enabled = true\r\n```\r\n\r\n###### Research\r\n*Enter an [x] character to confirm the points below:*\r\n\r\n- [X] I have read the [support page](https://ankidroid.org/docs/help.html) and am reporting a bug or enhancement request specific to AnkiDroid\r\n- [X] I have checked the [manual](https://ankidroid.org/docs/manual.html) and the [FAQ](https://github.com/ankidroid/Anki-Android/wiki/FAQ) and could not find a solution to my issue\r\n- [X] I have searched for similar existing issues here and on the user forum\r\n- [X] (Optional) I have confirmed the issue is not resolved in the latest alpha release ([instructions](https://docs.ankidroid.org/manual.html#betaTesting))\r\n\r\n",
